          "id": "tldr-web-dev:2023-10-13:o008",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "OORT",
          "summary": "Oort is an interactive programming game that challenges players to write Rust code to manage a fleet of spaceships, each with various functions such as engines, weapons, radar, and communication systems. The game offers a range of ships, from small missiles to massive cruisers, for players to control and program. It’s a way for developers to practice Rust in an entertaining manner.",
